metadata.name: Seductive Reasoning by AI Corr[tion
metadata.description:
This is the first NFT release by System of one

Thank you for the people who support artists, it is deeply appreciated.

In the year 2023 the world is playing with AI

This piece is my impression of AI experiencing a little bit of our world.

Again, thank you for your support - consider gifting one to a friend - use it as a crypto discussion piece and bring your people to WEB3

Enjoy!
